name: High Quality Drone Bays
desc: The Wasp manufacturies in this ship are overclocked, allowing the ship to replace losses at an alarming rate. Reduces the rate at which the fighter replacement rate decreases due to fighter losses by 25%, and increases the rate at which it recovers by 25%.

name: Broadside Ammo Supply System
desc: The broadside heavy layout of the ship makes supplying ammunition towards weapon systems simpler and less resource intensive, allowing the ship to focus its resources towards other systems. Lowers ordenance cost of medium ballistics by 4.
